Par

March 31, 2016

bg

Description:

The color to be used for the background.

Mnemonic:

BackGround

par(bg = "blue")
plot(rnorm(100))

par(bg = "#F0F0F0")
plot(rnorm(100))

par(bg = "#DCE6EC")
plot(rnorm(100))

bty

mnemonic: Box TYpe

par(bty = "o")
plot(rnorm(100))

par(bty = "l")
plot(rnorm(100))

par(bty = "7")
plot(rnorm(100))

par(bty = "c")
plot(rnorm(100))

par(bty = "u")
plot(rnorm(100))

par(bty = "]")
plot(rnorm(100))

par(bty = "n")
plot(rnorm(100))

cex

par(cex = 2)
plot(rnorm(100))

par(cex = .5)
plot(rnorm(100))

cex.axis

par(cex = 1, cex.axis = 0.5)
plot(rnorm(100))

par(cex = 1, cex.axis = 2)
plot(rnorm(100))

cex.main

par(cex = 1, cex.main = 0.5)
plot(rnorm(100))

par(cex = 1, cex.main = 2)
plot(rnorm(100))

cex.sub

par(cex = 1, cex.sub = 0.5)
plot(rnorm(100))

par(cex = 1, cex.sub = 2)
plot(rnorm(100))
